<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1172358>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. (1–4) Mentum of Matabele and Lebia: (1) Bifid mentum of M. arabica Mateu, 1986 (2, 3) Mentum without epilobes and single median tooth Lebia s. str, (4) Mentum with epilobes L. spec.(5–6) Head of Lebia sp.: (5) Lebia melanacra (Chaudoir, 1878) (6) L. melanura (Dejean, 1831)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1172358/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1172366>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27–29. Habitus of Lebia and Matabele: (27) Syntype. L. natalensis Chaudoir, 1871 (28) L. spec. (29) M. arabica Mateu, 1986." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1172366/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1172368>
    dc:description "FIGURES30–37. Head and pronotum of Lebia: (30) L.auberti (Fairmaire,1892), (31) L.melanacra (Chaudoir,1878), (32) L. melanura (Dejean, 1831), (33) L. raeesae sp. n. (34) L. natalensis Chaudoir, 1871, (35) L. nilotica Chaudoir, 1871, (36) L. spec.(37) Matabele arabica Mateu, 1986." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1172368/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1172360>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–13. Tarsomere IV and tibiae of Lebia: (7, 13) Lebia melanacra (Chaudoir, 1878), (8, 12) L. melanura (Dejean, 1831), (10, 11) L.raeesae sp. n. (9) L. spec." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1172360/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1172362>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14–17. Labrum, clypeus and apex of elytra: (14) Lebia auberti (Fairmaire, 1892), (15) L. raeesae sp. n. (16) Lebia auberti (Fairmaire, 1892), (17) L.raeesae sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1172362/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1172370>
    dc:description "FIGURES38–42. Aedeagusof Lebia: (38) L.auberti (Fairmaire,1892), (39)L.melanacra (Chaudoir, 1878), (40) L.melanura (Dejean, 1831), (41) L.raeesae sp. n. (42) L. nilotica Chaudoir,1871." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1172370/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

